                                </div>
                                <p class="mt-3 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">Write a few sentences about product.</p>
                        </div>    

                        <div class="col-span-full mt-2">
                            <label for="thumbnail" class="block text-sm/6 font-medium text-gray-900">Product images</label>
